      "raw_text": "Organized labor will not sit idly\nby and permit the passage of the\nLos Angeles anti-picketing ordi-\nnance without protest.\n\n\nAt its meeting last night the Cen\ntral Labor council adopted yigor-\nGus protest against the measure and\nresolved to visit the citycouncil to-\nnight in a body to combat the meas\nure. Attorney L. o. Connor has\nbeen retained to appear against the\nordinance."
